Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:04.24,English,,0,0,0,,Legend has it that 400 years \N ago, Blaise Pascal made a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:04.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,传说在400年前，布莱斯·帕斯卡打了一个赌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:07.28,English,,0,0,0,,(Blaise) "I bet I can break \N this large barrel of water
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:07.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,(Blaise) 我打赌只要另加一升水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:10.12,English,,0,0,0,,with the weight of just one \N additional liter of water!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:10.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我就能把这个盛水的大桶撑破
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:12.00,English,,0,0,0,,(Heckler) "How would you do that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:12.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,(Heckler) 你会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.64,English,,0,0,0,,(Blaise) "I'll pour it into a long thin tube
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,(Blaise) 我会把它倒进这根细长的管子里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:18.44,English,,0,0,0,,and the tall column of water will create \N enough pressure in the barrel to burst it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:18.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后这管水就会在桶里产生足够的压强把它炸开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:21.84,English,,0,0,0,,(Heckler) "How could a little \N water create so much pressure?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:21.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,(Heckler) 这么一点水怎会产生那么大的压力呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:27.36,English,,0,0,0,,(Blaise) "Pressure is forced over area, so \N even a small force concentrated in a tiny area
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:27.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,(Blaise) 压强是作用在单位面积上的力 所以即使是集中在很小面积上微弱的力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:33.20,English,,0,0,0,,can create a huge pressure. This pressure applied \N at the top will squeeze the water in the barrel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:33.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也能产生很大的压强 施加在顶部的压强会挤压桶中的水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:37.04,English,,0,0,0,,which will then push outwards with \N a huge force bursting the barrel."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:37.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并形成一股强大的外推力把桶挤爆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:41.76,English,,0,0,0,,My historical research suggests that Pascal \N never actually tried bursting a barrel to test
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:41.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我的历史学研究表明帕斯卡其实没有试过炸桶来测试他的理论
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:47.28,English,,0,0,0,,his hypothesis... but we can! If he's right, we \N can burst even the strongest barrel with just
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:47.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是我们可以 如果他是对的 只要我们制作一根足够坚固的细长管
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:52.24,English,,0,0,0,,one liter of water, provided we build a long \N thin and strong enough tube to pour it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:52.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们仅需要倒进一升水就可以撑破最坚固的桶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.84,English,,0,0,0,,(Blaise) "Sacre bleu, I was right!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,(Blaise) 草 我是对的
